      "content": "i mean i know i should talk to my doctor and stuff but honestly my doctor is super dismissive and just tells me to \"wait it out\" which is getting old. if i just stopped the sertraline today and started the st johns wort tomorrow morning, would that be okay? i dont want to have to taper off or anything, maybe just do it overnight to get the zoloft out of my system faster",
